    "title": "Improve core portability boundaries",
    "body": "<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_BEGIN -->\n## 変更点\n- `src/storage/storageAdapter.ts` をアプリ固有キーから切り離し、プラットフォーム非依存の string key/value IF に整理\n- 既存の保存キーは `src/storage/appStorage.ts` の `APP_STORAGE_KEYS` に集約し、保存データ形式（`doseRecords`, `premiumState`）は維持\n- `src/core` 専用の `tsconfig.core.json` と `typecheck:core` を追加し、DOM/Chrome ambient types なしで純ロジック境界を検査\n- `docs/PORTING.md` に core/storage 境界と移植時の保存アダプタ方針を追記\n\n## build通過\n- `npm run build` 通過\n\n## permissions不変\n- `public/manifest.json` は未変更\n- `manifest_version` は 3 のまま\n- `permissions` は `[\"storage\"]` のまま、`host_permissions` 追加なし\n<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_END -->\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents/bc-6cfa78a4-6fda-472b-9a45-753493bfeda2\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" width=\"114\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-6cfa78a4-6fda-472b-9a45-753493bfeda2\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" width=\"131\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;</div>\n\n",
